com.camerontec.catalys.core.message

Class FastSendingTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.core.message.FastSendingTransformer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFromMessageTransformer, ISendingTransformer

    public class FastSendingTransformer
extends Object
implements ISendingTransformer
    This transformer is used when sending messages over FAST.

    If toStream is called, it will write the FAST bytes to the stream. If toObject is called, it will return the FIX bytes, for use in persistence, logging, or anything that needs the FIX bytes of a message.

    FIX Encryption is not supported by this transformer, or by the FAST libraries.

    Non strict-mode is also unsupported.
